to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0642\u0650\u0644 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u064a\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0627\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0623\u0641\u0652\u0636\u064e\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0625\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0648\u0627\u0644\u0633\u064e\u0651\u0645\u0627\u062d\u064e\u0629\u064f 516\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20150,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/10\/iman-jihad-sabr-samahah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38315,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Best deeds are faith, jihad, patience, tolerance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 10, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cO Prophet of Allah, which deed is best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cFaith in Allah, belief in Him, and jihad in His way.\u201d The man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I want\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38311,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/10\/07\/beauty-sabr-samahah\/","url_meta":{"origin":38315,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Beauty: Islam beautified by patient and tolerance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 7, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam is beautified by two qualities: modesty and tolerance for the sake of Allah, and not for anyone else.\u201d Source: al-Tamhi\u0304d li-Ibn 'Abd al-Barr 13\/318 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Ishbili \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20441,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/07\/sabr-iman-yaqin\/","url_meta":{"origin":38315,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Conviction: Patience half of faith, certainty all of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"'Alqamah reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cPatience is half of faith and conviction is faith in its entirety.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 9083 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u00a0\u0631\u0636\u064a \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0639\u0646\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064f \u0646\u0650\u0635\u0652\u0641\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0625\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u062